."]},{"name":"Currie","meanings":["Scottish: habitational name from Currie in Midlothian, first recorded in this form in 1230. It is derived from Gaelic <i>curraigh</i>, dative case of <i>currach</i> ‘wet plain, marsh’.","Scottish: habitational name from Corrie in Dumfriesshire or another place so named (see   Corrie  ).","Scottish form of Irish   Curry   or, in Arran, an Anglicized form of <b>Mac Mhuirich</b> (see   McMurray  )."]}]},{"name":"Helene","type":"FIRST","attribution":"Dictionary of First Names © Patrick Hanks and Flavia Hodges 1990, 2003, 2006.","meanings":["form of   Helen  , now in fairly frequent use in the English-speaking world, usually without the accents."],"variants":[{"name":"Helena","meanings":["form of   Helen  , used also in Germany, the Netherlands, Scandinavia, and Eastern Europe."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Helene Corrie was born in 1375, in Ayr, Ayrshire, Scotland. She had at least 1 son with William Corrie. She died in 1445, in her hometown, at the age of 70."},"et":{"1375–1445":"1375–1445","1378–1444":"1378–1444","1400–1460":"1400–1460","1445":"1445","1400":"1400","1444":"1444","1378":"1378","1375":"1375","1460":"1460","Ayr, Ayrshire, Scotland":"Ayr, Ayrshire, Scotland"},"fi":{"1375–1445":"1375–1445","1378–1444":"1378–1444","1400–1460":"1400–1460","1445":"1445","1400":"1400","1444":"1444","1378":"1378","1375":"1375","1460":"1460","Ayr, Ayrshire, Scotland":"Ayr, Ayrshire, Scotland"},"fr":{"1375–1445":"1375–1445","1378–1444":"1378–1444","1400–1460":"1400–1460","1445":"1445","1400":"1400","1444":"1444","1378":"1378","1375":"1375","1460":"1460","Ayr, Ayrshire, Scotland":"Ayr, Ayrshire, Écosse","lifeSummary":"Helene Corrie est née en 1375, à Ayr, Ayrshire, Écosse. Elle a eu au moins 1 fils avec William Corrie. Elle est décédée en 1445, dans sa ville natale, à l’âge de 70 ans."},"de":{"1375–1445":"1375–1445","1378–1444":"1378–1444","1400–1460":"1400–1460","1445":"1445","1400":"1400","1444":"1444","1378":"1378","1375":"1375","1460":"1460","Ayr, Ayrs